<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Synnabot Commands Documentation</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Welcome to the official documentation for your Discord bot. Here you'll find a comprehensive list of commands, their usage, and permissions.</p>
      <p class="subtitle">💡 Tip: Prefix <code>!</code> is required (e.g., <code>!ping</code>)</p>
      <div class="buttons" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <a class="button secondary" href="/">← Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="commands-preview">
      <h2>📜 Command List</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Command</th>
            <th>Description</th>
            <th>Usage</th>
            <th>Permissions</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>!ping</code></td><td>Replies with "Pong!"</td><td><code>!ping</code></td><td><span class="status-tag online">Everyone</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!hello</code></td><td>Replies with a greeting</td><td><code>!hello</code></td><td><span class="status-tag online">Everyone</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!add</code></td><td>Adds two numbers</td><td><code>!add 5 10</code></td><td><span class="status-tag online">Everyone</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!streamers</code></td><td>Lists all 🎬 Streamer users</td><td><code>!streamers</code></td><td><span class="status-tag online">Everyone</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!setbirthday</code></td><td>Set birthday for user</td><td><code>!setbirthday @User 29 03</code></td><td><span class="status-tag offline">Mod Only</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!birthday</code></td><td>Gets birthday of a user</td><td><code>!birthday @User</code></td><td><span class="status-tag online">Everyone</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!settimezone</code></td><td>Set timezone for a user</td><td><code>!settimezone @User UTC+6:30</code></td><td><span class="status-tag offline">Mod Only</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!time</code></td><td>Gets user’s current time</td><td><code>!time @User</code></td><td><span class="status-tag online">Everyone</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!settwitch</code></td><td>Link Twitch username</td><td><code>!settwitch @User &lt;username&gt;</code></td><td><span class="status-tag offline">Mod Only</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!streamlinks</code></td><td>List streamers and Twitch links</td><td><code>!streamlinks</code></td><td><span class="status-tag online">Everyone</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>!ask</code></td><td>Ask Gemini AI</td><td><code>!ask &lt;question&gt;</code></td><td><span class="status-tag online">Everyone</span></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="commands-preview">
      <h2>🛠️ Example Command Usage</h2>
      <pre><code>!ping
# ➜ Pong!

!hello
# ➜ Hello @Syn

!add 5 15
# ➜ The sum is 20

!setbirthday @Syn 29 3
# ➜ 🎉 Set birthday for Syn to 29 Mar

!settimezone @Syn UTC+6:30
# ➜ 🌍 Set timezone for Syn to Asia/Kolkata

!time @Syn
# ➜ 🕒 Time for Syn: Sunday, April 6th 2025, 4:15 PM (UTC+6:30)

!settwitch @Syn St_Synna
# ➜ ✅ Updated Twitch link for Syn to St_Synna

!streamlinks
# ➜ 
Discord User (ID)             | Twitch Username
-----------------------------------------------
azakenR (867113282929557514)  | azakenr
Syn (953502362474000434)      | st_synna
kyoudai7 (972582587996455022) | kyoudai7

!ask What is the capital of France?
# ➜ The capital of France is Paris</code></pre>
    </section>

